events.name: Minnesota Golden Gophers at Purdue Boilermakers

headlines.description: — Zach Edey overcame a slow start with 24 points and 15 rebounds as No. 2 Purdue rallied from a 10-point deficit to defeat Minnesota 84-76 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 2 Purdue rallies from 10 down to beat Minnesota 84-76 behind Edey's 24 points and 15 rebounds

events.name: Pepperdine Waves at Saint Mary's Gaels

headlines.description: — Augustus Marciulionis scored a career-high 28 points and Alex Ducas beat the halftime buzzer with a halfcourt shot to lead No. 18 Saint Mary's to its 13th straight win, 103-59 over Pepperdine on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 18 Saint Mary's beats Pepperdine 103-59 for its 13th straight win

events.name: Temple Owls at Florida Atlantic Owls

headlines.description: — Johnell Davis scored 17 points, Alijah Martin and Brandon Weatherspoon each had 16 and No. 24 Florida Atlantic beat Temple 80-68 on Thursday night in a battle of the Owls.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 24 FAU wins battle of the Owls, topping Temple 80-68 in American Athletic
